## composer 错误总结

#### 错误

> [Composer\Downloader\TransportException]
> Your configuration does not allow connections to http://xx.xx.com. See https://getcomposer.org/doc/06-config.md#secure-http for details.

- [x] 解决方法禁用https请求，改用http方式。所以我们在composer.json文件中设置一个本地或全局的composer配置config
<span style="color:#D2691E">方法一</span>：命令行composer config secure-http false。通过命令修改composer.json，效果等同方法二。
<span style="color:#D2691E">方法二</span>：直接改composer.json,给“config”项中加上"secure-http": false  

```json
"config" : {    
        "vendor-dir" : "packages",  
        "secure-http": false    
}  
```
